{
  "id": "69c72e64f6cf6984d3e1d196",
  "title": "infobox日記",
  "created": 1774661228,
  "updated": 1777073288,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c72e64f6cf6984d3e1d196",
      "text": "infobox日記",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661228,
      "updated": 1774661228
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72e6c0000000000903ac4",
      "text": "infoboxで日記をつける",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661228,
      "updated": 1774661244
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72e6c0000000000903ac5",
      "text": "`YYYY-MM-DD`のページを作って、[infobox]を置く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661229,
      "updated": 1776245271
    },
    {
      "id": "69c730bf000000000014dd2a",
      "text": "`YYYY-MM-DD`のページにアイコンリンク用の画像を用意する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661823,
      "updated": 1774661852
    },
    {
      "id": "69c731b6000000000014dd2f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774662070,
      "updated": 1774662070
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72f5e0000000000903aca",
      "text": "infoboxに登録するには、`#YYYY-MM-DD`のページにリンクをつなげる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661470,
      "updated": 1774662117
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72fab0000000000903acb",
      "text": "#YYYY-MM-DD （infoboxに登録される）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661547,
      "updated": 1774662137
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72fac0000000000903acc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661549,
      "updated": 1774661549
    },
    {
      "id": "69c730e5000000000014dd2b",
      "text": "infobox以外の用途でリンクを使いたい場合は、アイコンリンクを使う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661862,
      "updated": 1776245293
    },
    {
      "id": "69c73159000000000014dd2e",
      "text": "このリンクはinfoboxから拾われない→[YYYY-MM-DD.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661977,
      "updated": 1774662041
    },
    {
      "id": "69c73140000000000014dd2d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661952,
      "updated": 1774661952
    },
    {
      "id": "69c73493000000000014dd31",
      "text": "日付形式のアイコンリンクによって、関連ページを増やさないで昨日、明日といった日付のリンクができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774662804,
      "updated": 1774662905
    },
    {
      "id": "69c73493000000000014dd32",
      "text": "例: [2026-03-11.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774662804,
      "updated": 1774663030
    },
    {
      "id": "69c73493000000000014dd33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774662804,
      "updated": 1774662804
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5ebe0000000000d531e5",
      "text": "[** infobox日記とは]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776246463,
      "updated": 1776246486
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5aa90000000000d531e1",
      "text": "　[井戸端日記]（[共同日記]）とは別の[共同日記]です",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776245418,
      "updated": 1776246708
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5adf0000000000d531e4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776245472,
      "updated": 1776245472
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5eda0000000000d531e6",
      "text": "[** infobox日記の特徴]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776246490,
      "updated": 1776246550
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5ef70000000000d531e7",
      "text": "　[infobox]（[文芸的データベース]）の機能を使った分散型アーキテクチャ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776246520,
      "updated": 1776246704
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5f190000000000d531e8",
      "text": "　日付ページ（`YYYY-MM-DD`のページ）に日記の一覧と概要が表示されるので、読みたい日記だけ読むことができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776246553,
      "updated": 1776247097
    },
    {
      "id": "69df651d0000000000d531ef",
      "text": "　code:mermaid",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248094,
      "updated": 1776248188
    },
    {
      "id": "69df65730000000000d531f0",
      "text": "  graph LR",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248179,
      "updated": 1776248194
    },
    {
      "id": "69df65730000000000d531f1",
      "text": "  M[日付ページ（YYYY-MM-DD）]---A[Aさんの日記（#YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248179,
      "updated": 1776248294
    },
    {
      "id": "69df65f80000000000d531f2",
      "text": "  M---B[Bさんの日記（#YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248312,
      "updated": 1776248331
    },
    {
      "id": "69df66300000000000d531f3",
      "text": "  M---C[Cさんの日記（#YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248368,
      "updated": 1776248381
    },
    {
      "id": "69df613a0000000000d531ea",
      "text": "　他人に遠慮せずに日記ページを編集することができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776247098,
      "updated": 1776247178
    },
    {
      "id": "69df67eb0000000000d53200",
      "text": "　 ページを小さく維持することができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248812,
      "updated": 1776248843
    },
    {
      "id": "69df680b0000000000d53201",
      "text": "　 必要とあれば長文も載せることができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248843,
      "updated": 1776248891
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0b7320000000000ab2da6",
      "text": "　 ネガティブなことでも書くことができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776334644,
      "updated": 1776334676
    },
    {
      "id": "69df61980000000000d531eb",
      "text": "　[トピック指向]と相性が良い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776247192,
      "updated": 1776334705
    },
    {
      "id": "69df61cd0000000000d531ec",
      "text": "　　トピック別に複数の日記ページを作成することができます",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776247245,
      "updated": 1776247307
    },
    {
      "id": "69df66700000000000d531f4",
      "text": "　　code:mermaid",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248433,
      "updated": 1776248447
    },
    {
      "id": "69df667f0000000000d531f5",
      "text": "    graph LR",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248447,
      "updated": 1776248447
    },
    {
      "id": "69df667f0000000000d531f6",
      "text": "    M[日付ページ（YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248447,
      "updated": 1776248463
    },
    {
      "id": "69df66860000000000d531f9",
      "text": "    M---A1[Aさんの仕事日記（#YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248454,
      "updated": 1776248527
    },
    {
      "id": "69df667f0000000000d531f7",
      "text": "    M---A2[Aさんのグルメ日記（#YYYY-MM-DD）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248447,
      "updated": 1776248536
    },
    {
      "id": "69df667f0000000000d531f8",
      "text": "  トピック別に分割できるので、ひとつのページが重くなる確率は低くなります",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248447,
      "updated": 1776250092
    },
    {
      "id": "69e1aa390000000000e589c4",
      "text": "  [トピック指向日記]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776396858,
      "updated": 1776396875
    },
    {
      "id": "69df5f190000000000d531e9",
      "text": "　ひとつの日記ページに複数の日付をいれることができる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776246554,
      "updated": 1776247387
    },
    {
      "id": "69df625b0000000000d531ee",
      "text": "　　`#YYYY-MM-DD`　は[ハッシュタグ]なので、ちがう日付のハッシュタグを複数書くことができます",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776247387,
      "updated": 1776247514
    },
    {
      "id": "69df62250000000000d531ed",
      "text": "　　code:mermaid",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776247334,
      "updated": 1776248604
    },
    {
      "id": "69df671b0000000000d531fb",
      "text": "    graph LR",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248604,
      "updated": 1776248604
    },
    {
      "id": "69df671b0000000000d531fc",
      "text": "    M1[日付ページ（YYYY-MM-01）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248604,
      "updated": 1776248621
    },
    {
      "id": "69df673a0000000000d531ff",
      "text": "    M2[日付ページ（YYYY-MM-02）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248634,
      "updated": 1776248653
    },
    {
      "id": "69df671b0000000000d531fd",
      "text": "    M1---A[Aさんの日記（#YYYY-MM-01 , #YYYY-MM-02）]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248604,
      "updated": 1776248701
    },
    {
      "id": "69df671b0000000000d531fe",
      "text": "    M2---A",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248604,
      "updated": 1776248712
    },
    {
      "id": "69df671a0000000000d531fa",
      "text": "[** infobox日記の書き方]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776248602,
      "updated": 1776337711
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0c31f0000000000094110",
      "text": "　まず、日記の[ページタイトル]を考えます",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776337695,
      "updated": 1776337785
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0c3610000000000094112",
      "text": "　ページを作ります",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776337761,
      "updated": 1776337802
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0c38a0000000000094113",
      "text": "　ページの中に記事を書きます",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776337802,
      "updated": 1776337846
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0c3b70000000000094114",
      "text": "　ハッシュタグ `#YYYY-MM-DD`をつけてinfobox日記に登録します",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776337847,
      "updated": 1776337937
    },
    {
      "id": "69ebfc6c0000000000a5dd2c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777073261,
      "updated": 1777073277
    },
    {
      "id": "69e0c3300000000000094111",
      "text": "[日付タグ] - [日付ページ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776337713,
      "updated": 1777073286
    },
    {
      "id": "69ebfc5a0000000000a5dd2a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777073243,
      "updated": 1777073243
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72e920000000000903ac6",
      "text": "[https://img.shields.io/badge/%23-infobox日記-white#.png]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661267,
      "updated": 1776567812
    },
    {
      "id": "69c72e930000000000903ac7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774661268,
      "updated": 1774661268
    }
  ]
}